comments: Harris (PHI) makes incidental contact with Lopez's (CHI) hand during the rebound and Lopez is able to come down with the ball.
Butler (PHI) makes marginal contact with Lopez's (CHI) body as he cleanly dislodges the ball.
Markkanen (CHI) moves laterally into Butler's (PHI) path in transition and the contact affects Butler's SQBR.
Lopez (CHI) extends his arms into Simmons (PHI) and delivers contact that affects Simmons' ability to defend the screen.
Butler (PHI) dislodges Dunn (CHI) from his position during the rebound.
Lopez (CHI) moves slightly as he absorbs contact when setting the pick in Simmons' (PHI) path but he does not prevent Simmons from disengaging from the contact.
Scott (PHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with LaVine (CHI) after the release on his jump shot attempt.
LLB shows Lopez (CHI) initiates arm contact with Simmons (PHI) during the rebound and Simmons does not clamp Lopez's arm.
Simmons (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Markkanen (CHI).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Simmons (PHI) loses possession and Scott (PHI) gathers the ball with a foot out of bounds.
Lopez (CHI) sets the screen in Simmons' (PHI) path and absorbs contact.
Lopez (CHI) sets the pick in Simmons' (PHI) path and does not deliver contact.
Scott (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during LaVine's (CHI) driving shot attempt.
RHH shows that Porter Jr. (CHI) makes contact with Harris' (PHI) hand that is on the ball during the driving shot attempt.
Lopez (CHI) sets the pick in Butler's (PHI) path and slightly extends his arms during contact. Butler is able to play through the contact and continue to defend.
Scott (PHI) makes contact to Lopez's (CHI) body during the drive but the contact is marginal.
LLS shows Lopez (CHI) extends his off-arm unnaturally and initiates the contact with Scott (PHI) during the shot attempt. Any contact initiated by Scott comes after the release of the shot.
Selden (CHI) briefly places his arm around Scott (PHI) but the contact is marginal and does not affect his FOM.
Harris (PHI) wraps Porter Jr. (CHI) during the inbound.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact to the arm of Butler (PHI) on the drive that affects his ability to gather the ball.
LLS shows Scott (PHI) makes contact to the head of LaVine (CHI) on the driving shot attempt.
Lopez (CHI) initiates contact with Scott (PHI) during rebounding but the contact is marginal.
After the initial inbound, the official communicated with the Replay Center and found that a clock malfunction had occurred. The crew correctly restored the 00:00.5 of remaining clock.
Markkanen (CHI) briefly defends Scott (PHI) with two hands during the inbound but does not affect his SQBR.
